sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Blazor
    participant API
    participant Service
    participant OpenAI as Azure OpenAI
    
    User->>Blazor: Enter text
    User->>Blazor: Click Translate
    Blazor->>API: POST /api/translation/translate
    API->>Service: TranslateAsync()
    Service->>OpenAI: Request translation
    OpenAI-->>Service: Victorian English text
    Service-->>API: Translation response
    API-->>Blazor: 200 OK
    Blazor->>User: Display translation
